{"tid":1771910,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"呢幾個月對你既人生有咩改變？","createTime":"2019-12-06T07:50:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T20:48:53.000Z","uid":302,"like":64,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"caaee69d2d0a71b0714a6342ad728e11a897e4ee","tid":1771910,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T07:50:35.000Z","msg":"半年前 我幾乎係金錢掛帥 間公司剩係做大野唔做細野 612之後差唔多全職發夢 間公司都冇接job咁濟<br />\n呢排經濟唔多掂就做返啲地區工作 主要服務下人咁<br />\n自己都唔再睇錢咁濟 反而多左時間陪下屋企人 做下家務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二就係對其他人包容性高左好多 尤其出街會對後生仔禮貌左 善意好多 因為總覺得佢有機會係發夢並肩作戰既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之成個人生睇法唔同左好多 覺得人生唔再係錢咁簡單 唔再重視物質 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eff2fecf703fa431ce82cc8c8916f702b51b6f2","tid":1771910,"uid":302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T07:53:17.000Z","msg":"快啲入後講下 調整好心態 準備下半場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd5bdcc9b88956a27943468022fa920e25a6714","tid":1771910,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T07:53:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>快啲入黎講下 調整好心態 準備下半場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0ae34236ee7922427b9f5487800c6216875a1819","tid":1771910,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T07:55:22.000Z","msg":"再一次加強我嘅係睇歷史度得出黎嘅果套結論<br />\n世界上無公義<br />\n但見到共產黨就快仆街<br />\n真係好開心"},{"pid":"de4ae91d08bae89ceb861882b6331c377a7fae5d","tid":1771910,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ae34236ee7922427b9f5487800c6216875a1819","tid":1771910,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T07:55:22.000Z","msg":"再一次加強我嘅係睇歷史度得出黎嘅果套結論<br />\n世界上無公義<br />\n但見到共產黨就快仆街<br />\n真係好開心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T07:58:32.000Z","msg":"可能未必現世報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif